title: Rookie Classes with the Biggest Impact in 2020
itunes:title: Rookie Classes with the Biggest Impact in 2020
description:
Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys examine what teams' offseason moves say about their roster-building strategies (2:23). Then, the duo do a deep dive on which rookie classes will have the biggest impact in the 2020 season (19:15).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
